=====================================
To compile sequential version type
make seq
for MPI version type
make mpi

executable - adda

=====================================
The input-files (read when executing)
1) avg_params.dat - orientation averaging
2) alldir_params.dat - Csca and asym calculations
3) scat_params.dat - calculation of scattering in many directions

4) -read filename
this command line option specifies dipole file to read
format:
#comments (several lines starting with '#')
Nmat=n             -  number of materials, if present - material index must be specified in following lines
x y z [ind]        -  integers; x,y,z - coordinates in scale of dipole size (>=0); ind - material index (>=1)
...many lines